review_text: The best Napoli style pizza in the city, better than Montana imo.
Great Thai spot with outdoor seating in a cool area of town
Great polish restaurant with delicious pierogies. Only spot in Frankfurt I could find
Somewhere between a bar and a club, this is the spot to go in Frankfurt for after work drinks or weekend shenanigans
